RAWALPINDI, Dec 23 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi on Friday visited the Combined Military Hospital (CMH) Rawalpindi to enquire about the health of security officers and soldiers who got injured while clearing the CTD complex in Bannu.
The president praised their bravery and resolve to fight against terrorism, a press release said.
